    <item>
      <title>芬兰 12 岁少年在学校开枪，造成 1 人死亡、2 人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-02/urgent-several-people-are-wounded-in-a-school-shooting-in-helsinki-and-police-have-detained-a-suspect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赫尔辛基（美联社）——警方称，周二上午，一名 12 岁学生向芬兰南部一所中学开枪，造成一名学生死亡，另外两名学生受重伤。嫌疑人后来被捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-02/urgent-several-people-are-wounded-in-a-school-shooting-in-helsinki-and-police-have-detained-a-suspect</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:41:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰无人机袭击俄罗斯腹地鞑靼斯坦地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/drones-strike-russia-s-tatarstan-region-far-from-ukraine-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二早些时候，乌克兰无人机自入侵开始以来首次袭击了俄罗斯鞑靼斯坦地区，击中目标包括距离两国边境近 1,500 公里（约 930 英里）的一座炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/drones-strike-russia-s-tatarstan-region-far-from-ukraine-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 07:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗哈梅内伊誓言在叙利亚致命袭击后惩罚以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗在指责以色列对其驻叙利亚大使馆发动致命空袭后发誓要对以色列进行报复——这是双方因加沙战争而不断升级的代理人冲突中罕见的直接对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:11:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将扩大预算缺口 42 亿美元以刺激经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁已批准一项计划，将明年的预算赤字目标扩大约42亿美元，以帮助刺激东南亚第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/thailand-to-widen-2025-budget-gap-by-4-2-billion-to-spur-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 04:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
